product.name: 4-Light Black Orb Chandelier, 20" Black and Gold Globe Pendant Light, Adjustable Hanging Ceiling Light Fixtures, Industrial Ceiling Chandelier Light for Kitchen, Dining Room, Foyer
product.description:
Treekee is committed to developing and manufacturing high-quality, green energy-saving lighting products to meet your lighting experience and enhance your quality of life.
Our product range includes outdoor, household, commercial, office, and traditional lighting.
Treekee is committed to the core belief of "serving every customer with care, bringing brightness to your home," continuously striving for excellence to create superior products.
product.bullet_points:
• Black and Gold Orb Chandelier: This dining room chandelier is a antique round frame, and the perfect sofe gold plating finished and the glass covers for the whole place gives bright and brilliant color. This antique light add brilliant for your home
• Height Adjustable: Measuring L20.4" * W20.4" * H22.4", this foyer lighting fixture features a 42-inch chain with an adjustable cord length to best suit your home decor. It is also adaptable for sloped ceilings
• 4*E12 Socket: Our entryway light fixture is compatible with 4 maximum 60 watt candelabra E12 base bulbs. Also compatible with dimmable bulb and switch (Bulbs and switch are NOT included). Working Voltage is 120V, AC
• Easy Install & Widely Use: The package come with all mouting hardware for easy installation; This is the perfect pendent light for kitchen, dining room, living room, entry way, hallway or stairway. Repalcing old, outdated pendent lights is a affordable way to update room of your home
• After-sale Service: Every Treekee design is created with uncompromising attention to detail, using only the good components. If you have any questions, please consult us
